00:41:07.060 --> 00:41:08.380
I'm okay.
- Hold on tight.

507
00:41:08.460 --> 00:41:10.380
Hold on tight.
- Be well. thanks.

508
00:41:11.940 --> 00:41:13.380
His friends. his friends.

509
00:41:14.180 --> 00:41:15.900
What happened?
- Do you know him?

510
00:41:16.940 --> 00:41:18.740
Come with us. Abu Zaher.
Come.

511
00:41:22.540 --> 00:41:24.540
Well done. friends.
- Feel better.

512
00:41:27.340 --> 00:41:28.500
Goddammit. - Where is he?

513
00:41:29.140 --> 00:41:31.300
Steve. answer me.
Steve!

514
00:41:31.580 --> 00:41:33.980
Gabi. I think they arrested Steve.

515
00:41:39.020 --> 00:41:41.820
Are you sure the police arrested him?
- I don't know. I lost him.

516
00:41:42.100 --> 00:41:44.340
He got rid of the earpiece.
- He knows what to do when out of contact.

517
00:41:44.500 --> 00:41:47.580
Goddammit. - Okay. pack up and get
home. - Just watch your left. bro.

518
00:41:50.420 --> 00:41:53.300
Salaam alaikum. friends.
- Greetings. how are you?

519
00:41:53.420 --> 00:41:54.580
I'm looking for you.

520
00:41:55.300 --> 00:41:56.980
I wanted to thank you again.

521
00:41:57.740 --> 00:42:00.740
Sorry about the shirt.
They say blood doesn't come out in the wash.

522
00:42:00.820 --> 00:42:03.300
No. it does.
Hot water and soap.

523
00:42:03.380 --> 00:42:06.700
The main thing is I see you healthy
and whole. habibi. Praise be to God.

524
00:42:08.420 --> 00:42:12.580
You have a Jordanian accent.
- No. Palestinian from Balata.

525
00:42:12.700 --> 00:42:14.660
Near Nablus. You know it?

526
00:42:15.660 --> 00:42:16.820
Of course.

527
00:42:17.140 --> 00:42:18.540
Abu Zaher from Rafah.

528
00:42:18.980 --> 00:42:21.180
Amir Mahajna and Ali Masrawi.

529
00:42:21.300 --> 00:42:24.060
Nice to meet you. - Nice to meet you.
- The honor is mine.

530
00:42:24.860 --> 00:42:26.260
Are you new in France?

531
00:42:27.060 --> 00:42:29.540
A month. something like that.

532
00:42:30.620 --> 00:42:32.180
May I offer you a ride home?

533
00:42:32.260 --> 00:42:34.220
No. thank you. habibi. Thanks.

534
00:42:35.580 --> 00:42:37.900
Thanks to you I'm going to sleep
on a clean bed.

535
00:42:38.020 --> 00:42:39.660
not on a bed full of bedbugs.

536
00:42:39.820 --> 00:42:43.340
Wallah. thank you. Abu Zaher.
We live not far from here.

537
00:42:43.900 --> 00:42:45.740
Really. there's no need.

538
00:42:48.020 --> 00:42:49.700
Not only did you save my life.

539
00:42:50.340 --> 00:42:51.940
you're also treating me kindly.

540
00:42:53.820 --> 00:42:55.100
Please. get in.

541
00:42:55.180 --> 00:42:57.180
I want to have a quick word with you.
face to face.

542
00:42:57.380 --> 00:42:58.460
Open.

543
00:42:58.700 --> 00:43:00.940
Yalla. - Okay.

544
00:43:42.140 --> 00:43:43.420
Get them out.

545
00:43:46.340 --> 00:43:47.380
Get out.

546
00:44:03.140 --> 00:44:05.420
Hey. hey. what's with you?
What is this?

547
00:44:11.940 --> 00:44:13.180
What's your story?

548
00:44:14.860 --> 00:44:17.460
Are you working with the Jews? Huh?

549
00:44:18.140 --> 00:44:19.020
Answer me!

